CREATED:20210508T142221Z
DESCRIPTION:The Zoom Sprouts comprise some members from the long-time old-t
 ime Bloomington band the Bean Sprouts - and one rogue bluegrass-er :-). Fun
  dance moves have been created and adapted by our caller for a happy experi
 ence whether you’re dancing or sitting back to relax and enjoy. For anyone 
 wanting to play along on a musical instrument on zoom (but muted)\, prior t
 o each dance we’ll announce the tune as well as the key.&nbsp\;<br><br>Old 
 Time Tenor Banjo: David Ernst<br>Fiddlers: Marty Mundy and Diane Jung<br>Gu
 itar: Michael Lindeau (may also play an occasional fiddle tune)<br><br>Call
 er: Katie Zukof <br><span>&nbsp\;</span><br><span><span><span><span><span><
 span><span>---------- </span><br>&nbsp\;<br><span><span><span>If you'd like
  the Zoom link\, please email us at <span><span>at <a href="mailto:communic
 ations@bloomingtoncontra.org">communications@bloomingtoncontra.org</a></spa
 n></span>.</span></span></span><br><span><span><span>As of March\, all BOTM
 DG Wednesday dances begin at <b>8 p.m. Eastern</b>.</span></span></span><br
 >&nbsp\;<br><span><span><span>If you haven’t been to one of our online even
 ts\, you might be wondering what to expect! As our musicians play for us\, 
 and the caller calls\, you are welcome to dance with us in your own space\,
  play along with the musicians with your mic muted\, or just watch and list
 en. We also try to check in with everyone briefly each week. The music last
 s until about 8:45\, followed by the check-in.</span></span></span><br>&nbs
 p\;<br><span><span><span>Waltzes are easy to dance alone or with a partner.
  Up-tempo tunes will sometimes have <span>contra</span>-like calling\, but 
 for the times when there is no calling\, please feel free to dance along at
  home with <span>contra</span> moves of your choice. Or just boogie down to
  the amazing music!</span></span>&nbsp\; </span><br><br><span>----------</s
 pan><span><br></span><br><span>We are grateful for all donations\, and happ
 y to be able to keep paying our musicians and dance leaders during these un
 usual times. You can find our <a href="http://bloomingtoncontra.org/support
 -our-performers-during-the-covid-19-downtime/">PayPal donation button on ou
 r website</a>.&nbsp\;&nbsp\;&nbsp\; </span></span></span></span></span></sp
 an><br></span>
LAST-MODIFIED:20210517T173756Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Zoom Sprouts (David Ernst\, Diane Jung\, Marty Mundy\, Michael Lind
 eau)\, caller Katie Zukof
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
