DESCRIPTION:<span>S<span>ome local callers are meeting on a monthly basis t
 o try out and practice new dances. Our next meetup is Sunday\, June 5\, at 
 3 p.m. Dancers are welcome to come to help out by walking through and danci
 ng these new dances. Musicians are also welcome to come to play music. If y
 ou're a caller\, dancer or musician interested in joining\, please let one 
 of the new callers know or email communications@bloomingtoncontra.org.</spa
 n> Please note that we'll be meeting at a *new location* in June - contact 
 us for the address.</span>
