DESCRIPTION:A night of contra dancing featuring the energized\, psychedelic
  sound of ContraForce\, with Drew Delaware calling. Contra Force is a "hurr
 icane of wild\, energetic contra music that will leave you gasping for brea
 th and begging for more." ContraForce\, from South Carolina\, features fidd
 ler Andrae Raffield\, Joey Dorwart on handpan and percussion\, Jimi "Two Na
 ils" Peirano on guitar\, and fiddler/vocalist Karin Mcquade. ContraForce wi
 ll be joining us via prerecorded video. Our caller will be Drew Delaware fr
 om Toronto\, Canada\, an inventive and joyful caller who has called coast t
 o coast and beyond. Drew has been an early advocate for creative adaptation
 s of dance choreography for virtual dancing.<font><span><br></span></font><
 br><font><span>Join us using your computer or mobile device&nbsp\;for fello
 wship\, music\, and even some virtual dancing while we deal with the restri
 ctions due to the COVID-19 pandemic.&nbsp\; See our Email newsletter for de
 tails or contact <span><a href="mailto:communications@bloomingtoncontra.org
 ">communications@bloomingtoncontra.org</a></span><span></span></span></font
 ><br><font><span><span></span></span></font>
LAST-MODIFIED:20200901T021848Z
LOCATION:Zoom Event (please see BOTMDG newsletter or contact communications
 @bloomingtoncontra.org for link)
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Zoom Event: the energized\, psychedelic sound of ContraForce\, with
  Drew Delaware calling
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
