DESCRIPTION:We will sing the Bean King Ballad and eat Bean King cake to det
 ermine our next Bean King on Wednesday\, January 8\, during the break time 
 at our usual Wednesday night contra dance at Harmony School. If you would l
 ike a slice of cake that might contain the bean\, please be sure to be at t
 he dance by 8:15 when we start slicing the bean king cake. \n\n\nAs you mig
 ht already know\, the Bean King is an annual contra tradition dating back t
 o the 70s. The Bean King is responsible for throwing a few parties througho
 ut the year for the contra dance group.
LAST-MODIFIED:20250106T174831Z
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Bean King - ballad\, cake\, and crowning
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
