CREATED:20221205T194637Z
DESCRIPTION:<b>Bean King Party - Friday\, January 6\, 2023</b><br>Every yea
 r on Twelfth Night\, the 6th of January\, since 1976\, the dance group has 
 held a party to celebrate the new year and select the Bean King for the yea
 r. &nbsp\;The party will start with a potluck at 6:30 p.m. and proceed to t
 he singing of the ballad and the eating of the cake around with music and d
 ancing to follow. The person who finds the bean in their piece of cake beco
 mes the new Bean King and is responsible for organizing three or four seaso
 nal parties throughout the year.&nbsp\;The festivities will again be at the
  Baus Haus\, 1210 W 8th\, Bloomington.&nbsp\;<br>&nbsp\;<br>Formal invite:<
 br>&nbsp\;<br>Her Royal Highness\, Ruth\,<br>King of the Bean\, Has Decreed
  that the Annual<br>Bean King Party<br>will be held on Friday\, 6 January 2
 023<br><br>for the purpose of selecting the new<br>King of the Bean.<br><br
 >The party starts with a pot-luck at 18:30 (that's 6:30 pm for<br>those who
  prefer medieval time) with main dishes served<br>at 19:00 (7:00 pm). Can't
  come that early? That's OK.<br><br>Come when you can.<br>Attendees must be
  vaccinated for COVID<br><br>MUSIC beside the WOODSTOVE and<br>DANCING on t
 he hardwood dance floor\,<br>Singing the BEAN BALLAD\, and Eating the<br>CA
 KE to discover who will be the new King<br><br>Festivities will be held at 
 the<br>BAUS HAUS\, 1210 W. 8th<br><br>Bloomington\, Ind.<br><br>Directions:
  Go to the corner of 8th St. and Rogers St. Turn west onto 8th St.<br>Go up
  the hill\, down the hill\, and up the next hill. When the street ends\, yo
 u’re there.<br>1210 is the very last house.<br><br>Bring: A dish for the Po
 t-luck or your favorite Munchies\,<br>Beverage\, Dance shoes\, &amp\; Music
 al instruments.<br><br>For more info call Bill Baus\, 812-339-1210 (no text
 s)\,<br>or Email &lt\;Baus1210@gmail.com&gt\;<br><br>For the Bean Ballad te
 xt see <a href="http://bloomingtoncontra.org/bean-bal.htm">http://bloomingt
 oncontra.org/bean-bal.htm</a>
LAST-MODIFIED:20221228T201654Z
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Bean King Party
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
