CREATED:20210226T221003Z
DESCRIPTION:<span>The Mad Larks are a DJ Contra duo (Elliot Eckel and Nedra
  McNeil) based in Louisville\, KY. They spin danceable beats from oldies to
  techno\, deep house to ambient\, and a bunch in between. Vibe with us this
  week with Nedra calling.</span><br><span>&nbsp\;</span><br><span>---------
 - </span><br><span><span><span>&nbsp\;</span></span></span><br><span><span>
 <span>If you'd like the Zoom link\, please email us at <span><span>at <a hr
 ef="mailto:communications@bloomingtoncontra.org">communications@bloomington
 contra.org</a></span></span>.</span></span></span><span><span><span></span>
 </span></span><br><span><span><span>As of March\, all BOTMDG Wednesday danc
 es begin at <b>8 p.m. Eastern</b>.</span></span></span><br><span><span><spa
 n>&nbsp\;</span></span></span><br><span><span><span>If you haven’t been to 
 one of our online events\, you might be wondering what to expect! As our mu
 sicians play for us\, and the caller calls\, you are welcome to dance with 
 us in your own space\, play along with the musicians with your mic muted\, 
 or just watch and listen. We also try to check in with everyone briefly eac
 h week. The music lasts until about 8:45\, followed by the check-in.</span>
 </span></span><br><span><span><span>&nbsp\;</span></span></span><br><span><
 span><span>Waltzes are easy to dance alone or with a partner. Up-tempo tune
 s will sometimes have <span>contra</span>-like calling\, but for the times 
 when there is no calling\, please feel free to dance along at home with <sp
 an>contra</span> moves of your choice. Or just boogie down to the amazing m
 usic!</span></span>&nbsp\; </span><br><span></span><br><span>----------</sp
 an><span><br></span><br><span>We are grateful for all donations\, and happy
  to be able to keep paying our musicians and dance leaders during these unu
 sual times. You can find our <a href="http://bloomingtoncontra.org/support-
 our-performers-during-the-covid-19-downtime/">PayPal donation button on our
  website</a>.&nbsp\; <br></span>
LAST-MODIFIED:20210226T222349Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Zoom Event: Techno Contra with Nedra and the Mad Larks
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
