DESCRIPTION:Contra and waltzes with Meadowhawk (Claire Johnson\, Amanda Ram
 ey\, and Matt Turino)\, with calling by Meg Dedolph. In another Zoom contra
  first\, we are truly delighted to be able to welcome Meadowhawk (from Urba
 na\, Illinois) to our little home screens for this dance. With Claire and A
 manda on fiddle and Matt on guitar and feet\, Meadowhawk's traditional and 
 original tunes will have you flying around your dancing room - and Meg Dedo
 lph's skilled and friendly calling will tell you just where to fly!<br><br>
 <font><span>Join us using your computer or mobile device&nbsp\;for fellowsh
 ip\, music\, and even some virtual dancing while we deal with the restricti
 ons due to the COVID-19 pandemic.&nbsp\; See our Email newsletter for detai
 ls or contact <span><a href="mailto:communications@bloomingtoncontra.org">c
 ommunications@bloomingtoncontra.org</a></span><span></span></span></font><b
 r><font><span><span></span></span></font>
