CREATED:20201130T222332Z
DESCRIPTION:<br>Contra and waltzes with caller Nicholas Rockstroh to the mu
 sic of Cherylyn Geers\, aka the Unamused Kraken. Nicholas and Cherylyn come
  to us from Louisville\, KY. Cherylyn is a multi-instrumentalist singer-son
 gwriter and lifelong musician. She discovered contra dancing at the beginni
 ng of 2019\, played in the pickup band at Berea afterparties\, and is looki
 ng forward to her first official contra gig! And this is Nicholas's first Z
 oom contra\, but he has been calling for six years\, including for us here 
 in Bloomington. He is preparing a program of dances all of which are writte
 n or adapted specifically for online contra.<br><font><span>Join us using y
 our computer or mobile device&nbsp\;for fellowship\, music\, and even some 
 virtual dancing while we deal with the restrictions due to the COVID-19 pan
 demic.&nbsp\; See our Email newsletter for details or contact <span><a href
 ="mailto:communications@bloomingtoncontra.org">communications@bloomingtonco
 ntra.org</a></span><span></span></span></font><br><font><span><span></span>
 </span></font>
LAST-MODIFIED:20201130T222332Z
LOCATION:Zoom Event (please see BOTMDG newsletter or contact communications
 @bloomingtoncontra.org for link)
