DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://bloomingtoncontra.org/sugar-hill/">https://blo
 omingtoncontra.org/sugar-hill/</a><br> <br>Friday evening to Sunday noon. J
 ust outside of Bloomington\, Indiana\, on beautiful Lake Monroe at the love
 ly Ransburg Boy Scout Camp\, 7599 Waldrip Creek Rd\, Bloomington\, IN 47401
 .<br><ul><li>dancing\, live music</li><li>swimming\, beach activities<br></
 li><li>workshops - jamming\, square dancing in the lake\, singing\, English
  Country Dance\, and more!</li><li>meals and snacks provided all weekend lo
 ng</li><li>camping included in admission (or upgrade to a cabin)</li></ul><
 br>Everyone helps! Everyone signs up for a volunteer shift upon arrival. Pl
 us\, callers and bands can sign up to call/play on Friday night and enter a
  lottery to perform on Saturday!<br><br>Early bird price - only $55 !<br>$8
 0 after August 16.
