CREATED:20251124T205431Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us for an evening of caroling on Monday\, December 15! We’
 ll meet in the Harmony School parking lot at 6:15 p.m. and head out at 6:30
  p.m. to visit several homes of dancers and BOTMDG community members. A few
  volunteer drivers will help us travel as a group. Feel free to bring a non
 -messy snack to share. Song lyrics provided. RSVP to kylawargel@gmail.com (
 not required but it helps for planning). Come help spread some cheer!
