 >7:30-9:30 p.m.</li>   <li><strong>Location</strong>: Boys and Girls Club o
 f Bloomington\, 311 S Lincoln St\, Bloomington\, IN\, 47401</li>   <li><str
 ong>Entrance fee</strong>: by sliding scale donation\, with a suggested ran
 ge from $3 to $20. We hope that everyone will give at least something becau
 se the event is sustained by the community. We estimate that if everyone we
 re to give $10\, we would break even after paying the rental fee and the pe
 rformers. Donations may be made <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https
 ://bloomingtoncontra.us13.list-manage.com/track/click?u%3D0c065082be7e5f220
 20734e68%26id%3D298b3f55c0%26e%3D6f029e4d69&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=calendar&
