DESCRIPTION:At the home of Marie Deer. Calling and dancing begins at 3:00 p
 .m. Followed by late afternoon social time - bring light snacks / light ear
 ly supper things to share if you can. <em>Callers </em>(including aspiring 
 callers!) are invited to bring dances to practice teaching and prompting. <
 em>Dancers </em>are invited to walk through those dances\, dance them\, and
  give feedback to the callers. <em>Musicians </em>are invited to play music
  for the dances. <br><br>Questions? Contact kylawargel@gmail.com or mariede
 er1961@gmail.com
