CREATED:20210601T152051Z
DESCRIPTION:<span><span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><b>IN-P
 ERSON DANCE&nbsp\;</b></span></span><span><span></span></span></span></span
 ></span><br><span><span><span><span><span></span></span></span></span></spa
 n><br><span><span><span><span><span></span></span></span></span></span><br>
 <span><span><span><span><span></span></span></span></span></span><br><span>
 <span><span><span><span></span></span></span></span></span><br><span><span>
 <span><span><span></span></span></span></span></span><br><span><span><span>
 <span><span><b></b></span></span><span><span><span><b>7:30-8:15 p.m.\, </b>
 at the Big Shelter at Marci Jane Lewis Park\, 106 South Park Street\, in El
 lettsville - a very short drive from Bloomington! You're welcome to come ea
 rly to help set up or stay to help pack things up at the end.</span></span>
 &nbsp\; <span><span></span></span><span><span><b>Contra Line! or pods! or l
 istening and watching!</b> We know that everyone has their own comfort leve
 l - some people might want to keep the same partner all night\, some people
  might not want to hug others\, some people might want to dance only in a s
 mall group of 3-4\, etc. We want to be <i>even more</i> <span><span><span>r
 espectful than usual of individual boundaries and take nothing for granted 
 about people's consent. Coming to listen and watch is an option&nbsp\; and 
 that there is plenty of space for that as well!</span></span></span></span>
 </span></span><br><span><span><br></span></span><br><span><span><b>TONS OF 
 FUN AND HAPPINESS • MUST BE VACCINATED •&nbsp\;MEMBERS ONLY • NO BATHROOMS 
 • NO ZOOM</b><br>&nbsp\;<br></span></span><br><span><span>This dance is run
  <b>by donation</b>\, with a suggested range from $3 to $20. We hope that e
 veryone will give at least something\, even if it's very little\, because t
 he event is sustained by the community. We will continue to give 100% of th
 e donations to the performers.</span></span>&nbsp\;<br><span><span>And reme
 mber:<br>- we will need your vaccination card or a photo of it if you haven
 't already sent us a photo (please bring in person if not already sent by t
 he end of Tuesday)<br>- if you haven't joined as a member yet\, you still c
 an do so online at&nbsp\;<a href="http://bloomingtoncontra.org/become-a-mem
 ber/">http://bloomingtoncontra.<u></u>org/become-a-member/</a><br>- Donatio
 ns very welcome to pay our performers:&nbsp\;<br><a href="http://bloomingto
 ncontra.org/support-our-performers-during-the-covid-19-downtime/">http://bl
 oomingtoncontra.org/<u></u>support-our-performers-during-<u></u>the-covid-1
 9-downtime/</a></span></span><p><span><span>- no bathrooms\, no alcohol\, n
 o Zoom\, sorry\, but lots of music and dancing and togetherness</span></spa
 n></p><p><span><span>- if it's raining\, the dance will go on - if it's thu
 ndering\, we will have to see (but come on out so we can figure it out toge
 ther): We will gather at the start\, and do a Rain\, Rain\, Go Away dance s
 o the show can go on!</span></span></p>&nbsp\; </span><br></span></span>
LAST-MODIFIED:20210608T222721Z
