CREATED:20201113T024741Z
DESCRIPTION:Contra and waltzes with Martha Edwards on fiddle and Bob Green 
 calling\, coming to us from St. Louis. We are so happy to welcome Martha an
 d Bob back again\, coming to us from their St. Louis living room\, where Bo
 b's calling and Martha's identical twin fiddles have enlivened many a danci
 ng night and set many a toe to tapping! Fun fact: in all the many times you
  were happily dancing to Martha's music over the years\, did you ever know 
 she was a classical musician who had never even heard of contra dancing for
  the first 25 years she was playing professionally? Now\, of course\, Marth
 a is a dancer's musician\, playing for dances of many kinds. She and Bob ha
 ve been consistently creating community through dance\, creatively meeting 
 the challenge and pivoting to online dances when that became necessary. We'
 re so grateful! <br><br><font><span>Join us using your computer or mobile d
 evice&nbsp\;for fellowship\, music\, and even some virtual dancing while we
  deal with the restrictions due to the COVID-19 pandemic.&nbsp\; See our Em
 ail newsletter for details or contact <span><a href="mailto:communications@
 bloomingtoncontra.org">communications@bloomingtoncontra.org</a></span><span
 ></span></span></font><br><font><span><span></span></span></font>
LAST-MODIFIED:20201113T024742Z
LOCATION:Zoom Event (please see BOTMDG newsletter or contact communications
 @bloomingtoncontra.org for link)
