UID:123cev5fnqc6iftlu72cfp625d@google.com
CREATED:20210508T142048Z
DESCRIPTION:<span>Jared Kirkpatrick is a dancer\, multi-instrumentalist\, c
 omposer\, and Jazz vibraphone student.  Jared will line up some beats perfe
 ct for Zoom dancing.  Meg Dedolph is a Chicago-area dance caller with a dee
 ply weird repertoire\, which allows her to call contra dances for rooms ful
 l of enthusiasts and newcomers\, to teach Irish set dances at Morris dance 
 weekends or to call a night of unplanned triplets during a snowstorm.</span
 ><br><span>&nbsp\;</span><br><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>----
 ------ </span><br>&nbsp\;<br><span><span><span>If you'd like the Zoom link\
 , please email us at <span><span>at <a href="mailto:communications@blooming
 toncontra.org">communications@bloomingtoncontra.org</a></span></span>.</spa
 n></span></span><br><span><span><span>As of March\, all BOTMDG Wednesday da
 nces begin at <b>8 p.m. Eastern</b>.</span></span></span><br>&nbsp\;<br><sp
 an><span><span>If you haven’t been to one of our online events\, you might 
 be wondering what to expect! As our musicians play for us\, and the caller 
 calls\, you are welcome to dance with us in your own space\, play along wit
 h the musicians with your mic muted\, or just watch and listen. We also try
  to check in with everyone briefly each week. The music lasts until about 8
 :45\, followed by the check-in.</span></span></span><br>&nbsp\;<br><span><s
 pan><span>Waltzes are easy to dance alone or with a partner. Up-tempo tunes
  will sometimes have <span>contra</span>-like calling\, but for the times w
 hen there is no calling\, please feel free to dance along at home with <spa
 n>contra</span> moves of your choice. Or just boogie down to the amazing mu
 sic!</span></span>&nbsp\; </span><br><br><span>----------</span><span><br><
 /span><br><span>We are grateful for all donations\, and happy to be able to
  keep paying our musicians and dance leaders during these unusual times. Yo
 u can find our <a href="http://bloomingtoncontra.org/support-our-performers
 -during-the-covid-19-downtime/">PayPal donation button on our website</a>.&
 nbsp\;&nbsp\;&nbsp\; </span></span></span></span></span></span><br></span>
LAST-MODIFIED:20210508T142510Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Techno contra by Jared  Kirkpatrick\, with caller Meg Dedolph
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
