DESCRIPTION:Contra dance chestnuts: old favorites\, called by Katie Zukof t
 o tunes by Supertrad (Eric Schedler and Sam Bartlett)\, with Claudio Buchwa
 ld. In celebration of the Thanksgiving month\, we will have an evening of o
 ld New England contra dance chestnuts\, to banjo\, accordion\, and fiddle. 
 Katie points out that traditional dances work particularly well for Zoom da
 nces\, as you get to be the active couple every time! Clear your living roo
 m\, break out your dance shoes and have some fun!! Excited to welcome back 
 Katie and Supertrad to our screens once again\, and to have Claudio with us
  for the first time at our virtual dance.&nbsp\; <br><br><font><span>Join u
 s using your computer or mobile device&nbsp\;for fellowship\, music\, and e
 ven some virtual dancing while we deal with the restrictions due to the COV
 ID-19 pandemic.&nbsp\; See our Email newsletter for details or contact <spa
 n><a href="mailto:communications@bloomingtoncontra.org">communications@bloo
 mingtoncontra.org</a></span><span></span></span></font><br><font><span><spa
 n></span></span></font>
LAST-MODIFIED:20201113T024624Z
LOCATION:Zoom Event (please see BOTMDG newsletter or contact communications
 @bloomingtoncontra.org for link)
