STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Ox on Fire - Tamara Loewenthal (fiddle)\, Rob Fischman (guitar)\, M
 ichael Valliant (bass)\, Jack Laskey (banjo)\, with Tammy Behrman calling 
