CREATED:20210601T152236Z
DESCRIPTION:<span><span><span><span><span></span></span></span><span><span>
 <span>Caller TBD </span></span></span></span></span><br><span><span><span><
 span><span><span><br><span><span><b>IN-PERSON DANCE&nbsp\;</b></span></span
 ><br><span><span><b>&nbsp\;</b></span></span><span><span><span><b>7:30-8:15
  p.m.\, </b>at the Big Shelter at Marci Jane Lewis Park\, 106 South Park St
 reet\, in Ellettsville - a very short drive from Bloomington! You're welcom
 e to come early to help set up or stay to help pack things up at the end.</
 span></span>&nbsp\; <span><span></span></span><span><span><b>Contra Line! o
 r pods! or listening and watching!</b> We know that everyone has their own 
 comfort level - some people might want to keep the same partner all night\,
  some people might not want to hug others\, some people might want to dance
  only in a small group of 3-4\, etc. We want to be <i>even more</i> <span><
 span><span>respectful than usual of individual boundaries and take nothing 
 for granted about people's consent. Coming to listen and watch is an option
 &nbsp\; and that there is plenty of space for that as well!</span></span></
 span></span></span></span><br><span><span><br></span></span><br><span><span
 ><b>TONS OF FUN AND HAPPINESS • MUST BE VACCINATED •&nbsp\;MEMBERS ONLY • N
 O BATHROOMS • NO ZOOM</b><br>&nbsp\;<br></span></span><br><span><span>This 
 dance is run <b>by donation</b>\, with a suggested range from $3 to $20. We
  hope that everyone will give at least something\, even if it's very little
 \, because the event is sustained by the community. We will continue to giv
 e 100% of the donations to the performers.</span></span>&nbsp\;<br><span><s
 pan>And remember:<br>- we will need your vaccination card or a photo of it 
 if you haven't already sent us a photo (please bring in person if not alrea
 dy sent by the end of Tuesday)<br>- if you haven't joined as a member yet\,
  you still can do so online at&nbsp\;<a href="http://bloomingtoncontra.org/
 become-a-member/">http://bloomingtoncontra.<u></u>org/become-a-member/</a><
 br>- Donations very welcome to pay our performers:&nbsp\;<br><a href="http:
 //bloomingtoncontra.org/support-our-performers-during-the-covid-19-downtime
 /">http://bloomingtoncontra.org/<u></u>support-our-performers-during-<u></u
 >the-covid-19-downtime/</a></span></span><p><span><span>- no bathrooms\, no
  alcohol\, no Zoom\, sorry\, but lots of music and dancing and togetherness
 </span></span></p><p><span><span>- if it's raining\, the dance will go on -
  if it's thundering\, we will have to see (but come on out so we can figure
  it out together): We will gather at the start\, and do a Rain\, Rain\, Go 
 Away dance so the show can go on!</span></span></p></span></span></span></s
 pan></span></span>
