 ngtoncontra.<wbr>org/become-a-member/</a>\, or you can bring $12 to the dan
 ce. Note: membership for anyone under 30 years old is only $2!</span><br><b
 r><span>Dances begin at <strong>7:30 p.m. Eastern</strong>. </span>The last
  waltz will conclude by 8:45 p.m. to allow time for cleanup. You are welcom
 e to come early to help set up or stay late to help pack up.<br><br>Events 
 will be in-person at the Big Shelter at <strong>Marci Jane Lewis Park</stro
 ng>\, 106 South Park Street\, in Ellettsville - just 15 minutes from downto
 wn Bloomington!<strong> </strong></span></span><br><br><span><span><span>Th
 is dance is run <strong>by donation</strong>\, with a suggested range from 
