DESCRIPTION:Fiddle tunes\, waltzes\, and polkas with the Bartlett family ba
 nd: Stefan\, Ruth\, and Wade Bartlett on fiddles\, Stefan also on piano\, S
 am Bartlett on banjo\, and Abby Ladin on string bass. For Thanksgiving Eve\
 , we welcome back the talented and accomplished Bartlett family band\, play
 ing music for dancing: fiddle tunes\, waltzes\, and polkas. They borrow fro
 m American old-time\, Irish\, English\, and klezmer traditions\, as well as
  playing music from friends who write in these traditions. The kids (Stefan
 \, Ruth\, and Wade) have been playing music their whole lives\, beginning t
 heir musical upbringing with a cocktail of old-time fiddle conventions and 
 the IU String Academy. Abby and Sam have also been involved with traditiona
 l music and dance most of their lives\, and are an important part of Bloomi
 ngton’s long history of traditional music.<a href="https://www.woosterdance
 .com/susan-english"></a><br><br><font><span>Join us using your computer or 
 mobile device&nbsp\;for fellowship\, music\, and even some virtual dancing 
 while we deal with the restrictions due to the COVID-19 pandemic.&nbsp\; Se
 e our Email newsletter for details or contact <span><a href="mailto:communi
 cations@bloomingtoncontra.org">communications@bloomingtoncontra.org</a></sp
 an><span></span></span></font><br><font><span><span></span></span></font>
LAST-MODIFIED:20201113T025038Z
LOCATION:Zoom Event (please see BOTMDG newsletter or contact communications
 @bloomingtoncontra.org for link)
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Zoom Event: The Bartlett Family Band - Fiddle tunes\, waltzes\, and
  polkas
TRANSP:OPAQUE
