 bring money to the dance. Annual membership is $12 (or only $2 per year for
  those under 30).<br><br><strong>Masks are required. </strong>Masks must co
 ver the mouth and nose at all times. Dancers can step outside for a mask br
 eak or may step into the hallway to take a drink of water.<br><br>This danc
 e is run <strong>by donation</strong>\, with a suggested range from $3 to $
 20. We hope that everyone will give at least something because the event is
  sustained by the community. We estimate that if everyone were to give $10\
 , we would break even after paying the rental fee and the performers. Donat
 ions may be made <a href="http://bloomingtoncontra.org/support-our-performe
 rs-during-the-covid-19-downtime/">online</a> or at the door.</span></span>
