UID:7gv7snele35s4l5p7f4cebm0mf@google.com
CREATED:20210601T152016Z
DESCRIPTION:<span><span><b>IN-PERSON DANCE&nbsp\;</b></span></span><br><spa
 n><span><b>&nbsp\;</b></span></span><span><span><span><b>7:30-8:15 p.m.\, <
 /b>at the Big Shelter at Marci Jane Lewis Park\, 106 South Park Street\, in
  Ellettsville - a very short drive from Bloomington! You're welcome to come
  early to help set up or stay to help pack things up at the end.</span></sp
 an><span><span>&nbsp\; </span></span><span><span><b></b></span></span><span
 ><span><b>Contra Line! or pods! or listening and watching!</b> We know that
  everyone has their own comfort level - some people might want to keep the 
 same partner all night\, some people might not want to hug others\, some pe
 ople might want to dance only in a small group of 3-4\, etc. We want to be 
 <i>even more</i> <span><span><span>respectful than usual of individual boun
 daries and take nothing for granted about people's consent. Coming to liste
 n and watch is an option&nbsp\; and that there is plenty of space for that 
 as well!</span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span></span></span
 ><br><span><span><br></span></span><br><span><span><b>TONS OF FUN AND HAPPI
 NESS • MUST BE VACCINATED •&nbsp\;MEMBERS ONLY • NO BATHROOMS • NO ZOOM</b>
 <br>&nbsp\;<br></span></span><br><span><span>This dance is run <b>by donati
 on</b>\, with a suggested range from $3 to $20. We hope that everyone will 
 give at least something\, even if it's very little\, because the event is s
 ustained by the community. We will continue to give 100% of the donations t
 o the performers.</span></span><br><span><span>&nbsp\;</span></span><br><sp
 an><span>And remember:<br>- we will need your vaccination card or a photo o
 f it if you haven't already sent us a photo (please bring in person if not 
 already sent by the end of Tuesday)<br>- if you haven't joined as a member 
 yet\, you still can do so online at&nbsp\;<a href="http://bloomingtoncontra
 .org/become-a-member/">http://bloomingtoncontra.<u></u>org/become-a-member/
 </a><br>- Donations very welcome to pay our performers:&nbsp\;<br><a href="
 http://bloomingtoncontra.org/support-our-performers-during-the-covid-19-dow
 ntime/">http://bloomingtoncontra.org/<u></u>support-our-performers-during-<
 u></u>the-covid-19-downtime/</a></span></span><p><span><span>- no bathrooms
 \, no alcohol\, no Zoom\, sorry\, but lots of music and dancing and togethe
 rness</span></span></p><p><span><span>- if it's raining\, the dance will go
  on - if it's thundering\, we will have to see (but come on out so we can f
 igure it out together): We will gather at the start\, and do a Rain\, Rain\
 , Go Away dance so the show can go on!</span></span></p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20210607T192635Z
