UID:7n4q0cacsdiu54au8ldtfkuf56@google.com
CREATED:20230416T204054Z
DESCRIPTION:<p>This workshop reviews and builds on what was taught in the f
 irst one on March 5th.<br><b> </b></p><p><b>Sunday\, April 23rd</b>\, at th
 e Harmony School gym (909 E 2nd St\, Bloomington\, IN).<br><br><b>2 to 3 p.
 m.: Waltzing Workshop</b> led by Tamara Loewenthal (for beginning and inter
 mediate waltzers)<br><br><b>3 to 4 p.m.: Open Waltzing</b>\, with Open Band
  hosted by Eric Schedler (for all levels of waltzers)\, all musicians welco
 me.</p><p>-------<br> </p><p>You are welcome to come for the workshop\, the
  open waltzing\, or both\, as you would like. You can come on both dates or
  just one or the other. <br><br>Doors will open at 1:40\; please come early
  to sign in\, show your proof of vaccination (if non-member)\, take off you
 r coat and change your shoes\, and whatever else you need to do to be ready
  for the workshop at 2:00!<br> </p><p>------<br> </p><p>*Special event\, me
 mbership not required</p><p>*Donation of $3 to $20 requested to help cover 
 hall rental and instructor</p><p>*Vaccination protocols: non-members please
  bring proof of bivalent booster (or most recent booster if not yet eligibl
 e for bivalent)</p><p>*Masks encouraged but not required<br><br>Come waltz 
 with us\, and invite your friends!</p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20230420T183846Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Waltzing Workshop and Open Waltzing
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
