 yla Wargel!</span><br><span><br></span><br><span>Flavors of Old Time\, Iris
 h\, Bluegrass tunes\, and a very old English waltz with The Bottom Dogs (Di
 ane Jung and Michael Lindeau): For lovers of contra dancing\, waltzing\, an
 d freestyle dancing. Diane and Michael will play most tunes as twin fiddles
  with a dynamic blend of their two different styles.</span><br><br><font><s
 pan>Join us using your computer or mobile device&nbsp\;for fellowship\, mus
 ic\, and even some virtual dancing while we deal with the restrictions due 
 to the COVID-19 pandemic.&nbsp\; See our Email newsletter for details or co
 ntact <span><a href="mailto:communications@bloomingtoncontra.org">communica
 tions@bloomingtoncontra.org</a></span><span></span></span></font><font><spa
 n><span></span></span></font>
