DESCRIPTION:<span><span><span><strong><span><span><span><span><span><strong
 >Weekly Wednesday Dance Information</strong></span></span></span></span></s
 pan></strong><span><span><ul><li><span><span>7:30-9 p.m.</span></span></li>
