 ass will be taught by Bloomington musician<span> </span><a href="https://ww
 w.google.com/url?q=https://sambartlett.com/music/&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=cal
 endar&amp\;usd=2&amp\;usg=AOvVaw19_CijX1-nqINy_N6onWB5" target="_blank"><sp
 an>Sam Bartlett</span></a>\,<span> </span>and will include practicing dance
  band skills and learning tunes<span> </span>appropriate for contra dances 
 in the old-time\, Irish\, and New England<span> </span>traditions. Particip
 ants should have familiarity with their instrument\; all levels are welcome
 .</span>  <br><br><span>The<span> </span>registration fee is on a sliding s
