 rmance. Classes are 6-7 p.m. at Harmony<span> </span>School\, in the 3rd/4t
 h classroom.</span><br><span> </span><br><p><b><span>Classes are 6-7 p.m. a
 t Harmony School in the 3rd/4th classroom on the following dates:</span></b
 ><span><u></u><u></u></span></p><ul><li><span>Sept 18<u></u><u></u></span><
 /li><li><span>Sept 25<u></u><u></u></span></li><li><i><span>No class Oct 2<
