BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART:20210623T233000Z
DTEND:20210624T004500Z
DTSTAMP:20260309T020722Z
UID:6p9ms2h2q1cid859enp4op77ek@google.com
CREATED:20210601T152145Z
DESCRIPTION:<span><span>Caller TBD<span><span><b> <br></b></span></span></s
 pan></span><br><span><span><span><span><b>&nbsp\;</b></span></span></span><
 /span><br><span><span><span><span><b>IN-PERSON DANCE&nbsp\;</b></span></spa
 n><br><span><span><b>&nbsp\;</b></span></span><span><span><span><b>7:30-8:1
 5 p.m.\, </b>at the Big Shelter at Marci Jane Lewis Park\, 106 South Park S
 treet\, in Ellettsville - a very short drive from Bloomington! You're welco
 me to come early to help set up or stay to help pack things up at the end.<
 /span></span>&nbsp\; <span><span></span></span><span><span><b>Contra Line! 
 or pods! or listening and watching!</b> We know that everyone has their own
  comfort level - some people might want to keep the same partner all night\
 , some people might not want to hug others\, some people might want to danc
 e only in a small group of 3-4\, etc. We want to be <i>even more</i> <span>
 <span><span>respectful than usual of individual boundaries and take nothing
  for granted about people's consent. Coming to listen and watch is an optio
 n&nbsp\; and that there is plenty of space for that as well!</span></span><
 /span></span></span></span><br><span><span><br></span></span><br><span><spa
 n><b>TONS OF FUN AND HAPPINESS • MUST BE VACCINATED •&nbsp\;MEMBERS ONLY • 
 NO BATHROOMS • NO ZOOM</b><br>&nbsp\;<br></span></span><br><span><span>This
  dance is run <b>by donation</b>\, with a suggested range from $3 to $20. W
 e hope that everyone will give at least something\, even if it's very littl
 e\, because the event is sustained by the community. We will continue to gi
 ve 100% of the donations to the performers.</span></span>&nbsp\;<br><span><
 span>And remember:<br>- we will need your vaccination card or a photo of it
  if you haven't already sent us a photo (please bring in person if not alre
 ady sent by the end of Tuesday)<br>- if you haven't joined as a member yet\
 , you still can do so online at&nbsp\;<a href="http://bloomingtoncontra.org
 /become-a-member/">http://bloomingtoncontra.<u></u>org/become-a-member/</a>
 <br>- Donations very welcome to pay our performers:&nbsp\;<br><a href="http
 ://bloomingtoncontra.org/support-our-performers-during-the-covid-19-downtim
 e/">http://bloomingtoncontra.org/<u></u>support-our-performers-during-<u></
 u>the-covid-19-downtime/</a></span></span><p><span><span>- no bathrooms\, n
 o alcohol\, no Zoom\, sorry\, but lots of music and dancing and togethernes
 s</span></span></p><p><span><span>- if it's raining\, the dance will go on 
 - if it's thundering\, we will have to see (but come on out so we can figur
 e it out together): We will gather at the start\, and do a Rain\, Rain\, Go
  Away dance so the show can go on!</span></span></p></span><span><span><spa
 n></span></span></span></span>
LAST-MODIFIED:20210608T222739Z
