DESCRIPTION:<br>Contra and waltzes with Wendy Graham calling to the music o
 f Peregrine Road. Start your night before New Year's Eve off right! Come pr
 epared to dance a little harder\, stay up a little longer\, get your holida
 y started early. Peregrine Road is Rachel Bell on accordion and Karen Axelr
 od on piano\, a high-energy\, quirky\, dreamy\, fiery duo that will "keep y
 our contra dance feet going all night long." Wendy Graham is a self-describ
 ed dance maniac who leads dances all over the country and as far away as En
 gland and Denmark. Come dance!<br><font><span>Join us using your computer o
 r mobile device&nbsp\;for fellowship\, music\, and even some virtual dancin
 g while we deal with the restrictions due to the COVID-19 pandemic.&nbsp\; 
 See our Email newsletter for details or contact <span><a href="mailto:commu
 nications@bloomingtoncontra.org">communications@bloomingtoncontra.org</a></
 span><span></span></span></font><br><font><span><span></span></span></font>
