 ies will start at 18:30 (that’s 6:30 pm<br>medieval time) with a pot luck d
 inner\, followed by music and dancing on the<br>hardwood dance floor.<br><b
 r>Bring your dance shoes\, musical instruments\, a pot luck dish or snack t
 o share\,<br>and your favorite beverage.<br><br>Directions to the Baus Haus
 :  From the corner of 8th and Rogers\, go west\, up the<br>hill\, continue 
 down the hill and up the next hill. 1210 is the very last house.<br><br>For
  more info contact:<br><br>   Tom Morrison\, &lt\;<a href="mailto:TomMorris
 on7@gmail.com">TomMorrison7@gmail.com</a>&gt\;\, 812-320-1187\, or<br>   Bi
