DESCRIPTION:<br>Techno contra returns! With the Mad Larks (Elliot Eckel and
  Nedra McNeil)\, a DJ-contra Duo based in Louisville\, KY. As you probably 
 know\, here in Bloomington we are very committed to live contra music - but
  oh do we love techno contra too! We are happy to be able to bring back the
  popular and exciting Mad Larks with their "super danceable energetic fun" 
 and their mashups from Pop to Electronic\, Classics to Deep House\, and a b
 unch in between. Featuring caller Nedra McNeil. <br><font><span>Join us usi
 ng your computer or mobile device&nbsp\;for fellowship\, music\, and even s
 ome virtual dancing while we deal with the restrictions due to the COVID-19
  pandemic.&nbsp\; See our Email newsletter for details or contact <span><a 
 href="mailto:communications@bloomingtoncontra.org">communications@bloomingt
 oncontra.org</a></span><span></span></span></font><br><font><span><span></s
 pan></span></font>
LAST-MODIFIED:20201130T222514Z
LOCATION:Zoom Event (please see BOTMDG newsletter or contact communications
 @bloomingtoncontra.org for link)
SEQUENCE:2
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Zoom Event: Techno contra with the Mad Larks (Elliot Eckel and Nedr
 a McNeil)
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
