DESCRIPTION:<span>Contra and waltzes with caller&nbsp\;</span><strong>Nicho
 las Rockstroh</strong><span>&nbsp\;to the music of&nbsp\;</span><strong>Che
 rylyn Geers\, aka the Unamused Kraken</strong><span>. Cherylyn is a multi-i
 nstrumentalist singer-songwriter and lifelong musician. She's performed eve
 rywhere from coffee shops and farmers markets to marathons and the Cincinna
 ti Art Museum. She discovered contra dancing at the beginning of 2019\, pla
 yed in the pickup band at Berea after-parties\, and is looking forward to p
 laying another Bloomington Zoom Contra! Nicholas is excited to be returning
  to Bloomington's Zoom for another set of exciting\, original Zoom dances.<
 /span><span></span><span></span><br><br><font><span>Join us using your comp
 uter or mobile device&nbsp\;for fellowship\, music\, and even some virtual 
 dancing while we deal with the restrictions due to the COVID-19 pandemic.&n
 bsp\; See our Email newsletter for details or contact <span><a href="mailto
 :communications@bloomingtoncontra.org">communications@bloomingtoncontra.org
 </a></span><span></span></span></font><br><font><span><span></span></span><
 /font>
