DESCRIPTION:Contra and waltzes with Supertrad (Eric Schedler and Sam Bartle
 tt)\, with calling by Seth Tepfer from Atlanta. Our very own Supertrad\, pl
 aying together for us for the first time since we started our Zoom dances\,
  is "a tour de force of traditional dance music and the finest accordion/ba
 njo duo in the midwest. Though they are steeped in the subtle intricacies o
 f the old Irish and New England tune traditions\, they play with a groove a
 nd persistence that is more akin to the pulse of modern music." And we're e
 xcited to have Seth Tepfer\, "Atlanta's dance magician\," calling for us. C
 ome on out and dance!<font><span><br></span></font><br><font><span>Join us 
 using your computer or mobile device&nbsp\;for fellowship\, music\, and eve
 n some virtual dancing while we deal with the restrictions due to the COVID
 -19 pandemic.&nbsp\; See our Email newsletter for details or contact <span>
 <a href="mailto:communications@bloomingtoncontra.org">communications@bloomi
 ngtoncontra.org</a></span><span></span></span></font><br><font><span><span>
 </span></span></font>
