DTEND:20210520T010000Z
DTSTAMP:20260309T020722Z
UID:18uqlpdcob35jkhfkduj7tjhld@google.com
CREATED:20210508T142131Z
DESCRIPTION:<span>Beverley Street is a new band of veteran rockin' contra d
 ance musicians (from Staunton VA)\, who will get your feet moving and heart
  rate up with their energetic and eclectic array of Celtic\, Old Time and O
 riginal tunes! Janie and Allan (from Coracree) and Bill (The Bouncers) have
  all played for too numerous to mention dances in the US and Abroad!&nbsp\;
 </span><br><span>&nbsp\;</span><br><span>THE JANINE SMITH EXPERIENCE is wha
 t you get when you cross a howdy-ma'am-BBQ-and-beans honky tonk with Zoom c
 ontra and sprinkle on some twinkly lights for sass. She'll bring you a nigh
 t of fun dances\, from squares to contras\, heck maybe a singing square\, w
 hether you're sitting\, standing\, or somewhere in between. Her teaching is
  clear and to-the-point\, though she has been known to goof around a bit.</
 span><br><span>&nbsp\;</span><br><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>
 ---------- </span><br>&nbsp\;<br><span><span><span>If you'd like the Zoom l
 ink\, please email us at <span><span>at <a href="mailto:communications@bloo
 mingtoncontra.org">communications@bloomingtoncontra.org</a></span></span>.<
 /span></span></span><br><span><span><span>As of March\, all BOTMDG Wednesda
 y dances begin at <b>8 p.m. Eastern</b>.</span></span></span><br>&nbsp\;<br
 ><span><span><span>If you haven’t been to one of our online events\, you mi
 ght be wondering what to expect! As our musicians play for us\, and the cal
 ler calls\, you are welcome to dance with us in your own space\, play along
  with the musicians with your mic muted\, or just watch and listen. We also
  try to check in with everyone briefly each week. The music lasts until abo
 ut 8:45\, followed by the check-in.</span></span></span><br>&nbsp\;<br><spa
 n><span><span>Waltzes are easy to dance alone or with a partner. Up-tempo t
 unes will sometimes have <span>contra</span>-like calling\, but for the tim
 es when there is no calling\, please feel free to dance along at home with 
 <span>contra</span> moves of your choice. Or just boogie down to the amazin
 g music!</span></span>&nbsp\; </span><br><br><span>----------</span><span><
 br></span><br><span>We are grateful for all donations\, and happy to be abl
 e to keep paying our musicians and dance leaders during these unusual times
 . You can find our <a href="http://bloomingtoncontra.org/support-our-perfor
 mers-during-the-covid-19-downtime/">PayPal donation button on our website</
 a>.&nbsp\;&nbsp\;&nbsp\; </span></span></span></span></span></span><br></sp
 an>
LAST-MODIFIED:20210508T142524Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Beverley Street String Band (Janie Rothfield (fiddle)\, Allan Carr 
 (guitar) and Bill Wellington (mandolin\, banjo\, fiddle)) with caller Janin
 e Smith
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
