DESCRIPTION:His Royal Bean Highness\, Lennon\, King of the Bean\, announces
  that\, \nin accordance with his duties\, there will be a party on Saturday
 \, 2 \nNovember 2024\, at the Baus Haus\, 1210 W 8th St\, Bloomington\, IN.
  \nFestivities will start at 18:30 (that’s 6:30 pm medieval time) with \na 
 pot luck dinner\, followed by music and dancing on the hardwood \ndance flo
 or.\n\nBring your dance shoes\, musical instruments\, a pot luck dish or \n
 snack to share\, and your favorite beverage.\n\nDirections to the Baus Haus
 :  From the corner of 8th and Rogers\, go \nwest up the hill\, continue dow
 n the hill and up the next hill. \n1210 is the very last house.\n\nFor more
  info contact Lennon Beasley\, <LennonBeasley@gmail.com>\, \n812-606-7183 o
 r Bill Baus <Baus1210@gmail.com>\, 812-339-1210 (no \ntext).
LAST-MODIFIED:20241031T130630Z
