 > on respect and consent.</li></ul><strong>Covid Policies</strong>   <br><u
 l><li><strong>Membership Requirement</strong>: Becoming a member is easy! M
 embership is optional the first two times someone attends the dance in 2023
 .<br>   1) Fill out a membership form at the dance.<br>   2) Pay $10 either
  at the dance or <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://bloomingtonc
 ontra.us13.list-manage.com/track/click?u%3D0c065082be7e5f22020734e68%26id%3
