 and keyboard). We are happy to welcome our own Twy and John\, of Bloomingto
 n\, back to our Zoom dance\, with their unusual instruments (their "intrigu
 ing musical menagerie") and their intense and lovely tunes. Twy will be cal
 ling and teaching some simple dances\, including mixers. <br><br><font><spa
 n>Join us using your computer or mobile device&nbsp\;for fellowship\, music
 \, and even some virtual dancing while we deal with the restrictions due to
  the COVID-19 pandemic.&nbsp\; See our Email newsletter for details or cont
 act <span><a href="mailto:communications@bloomingtoncontra.org">communicati
 ons@bloomingtoncontra.org</a></span><span></span></span></font><br><font><s
 pan><span></span></span></font>
