DESCRIPTION:Come join us for a special afternoon and evening of dancing on 
 April 29th with music by the Cosmic Otters (<span>Meg Dedolph on guitar\, E
 ric Schedler on accordion\, and Johnathan Whittall on fiddle)</span><span> 
 and calling by Dan Blim.</span><br>3–5 p.m. English Country Dance<br>5–7 p.
 m. Dinner break (details forthcoming)<br>7–10 p.m. Contradance<br>Adults: $
 10 admission for either event\, $15 for both. <br>Children (under 16): $5 a
