DESCRIPTION:<span>Contra and waltzes with&nbsp\;</span><strong>The Trash Pi
 ckers</strong><span>&nbsp\;(Evan Copelly\, Myke Luurtsema\, and Kyla Wargel
 ). Evan (guitar\, vocals)\, Myke (banjo)\, and Kyla (calling\, ukulele) pla
 y pretty much all the old time tunes they know. The Trash Pickers bring for
 th a combination of charm and a strong dependence on the forgiving nature o
 f their audience. Kyla has been creating and adapting quarantine-friendly d
 ances since the 'rona was an adolescent. Take a break from dancing to real 
 old time musicians and get down with the Trash Pickers! </span><span></span
 ><span></span><span></span><br><br><font><span>Join us using your computer 
 or mobile device&nbsp\;for fellowship\, music\, and even some virtual danci
 ng while we deal with the restrictions due to the COVID-19 pandemic.&nbsp\;
  See our Email newsletter for details or contact <span><a href="mailto:comm
 unications@bloomingtoncontra.org">communications@bloomingtoncontra.org</a><
 /span><span></span></span></font><br><font><span><span></span></span></font
 >
