UID:1odglpkmoob8tk9gj1mij759o7@google.com
CREATED:20210328T145900Z
DESCRIPTION:<span>Dancing Through the Pundemic is Bob Green and Martha Edwa
 rds from St. Louis\, with contras\, English country dances and waltzes.&nbs
 p\;</span><br><span>&nbsp\;</span><br><span>Martha will be playing live\, a
 ccompanied by recorded versions of herself\, her son Alex\, and Stringdance
 r. Bob has put together a dance program tailored for a pundemic \, hits lik
 e:&nbsp\;</span><br><span>&nbsp\;</span><br><span>Salmon Chanted Evening – 
 original by Steve Zakon-Anderson&nbsp\;</span><br><span>Hands Solo – origin
 al by Bob Green&nbsp\;</span><br><span>Weave Well Enough Alone –original by
 &nbsp\;</span><br><span>Jim HemphillInvertro Flirtilization –original by Ji
 m Hemphill&nbsp\;</span><br><span>Dolphiniums and Daises – original by Tony
 a Rotenberg</span><br><span>&nbsp\;</span><br><span>&nbsp\;<span><span><spa
 n><span><br><span>---------- </span><br>&nbsp\;<br><span><span><span>If you
 'd like the Zoom link\, please email us at <span><span>at <a href="mailto:c
 ommunications@bloomingtoncontra.org">communications@bloomingtoncontra.org</
 a></span></span>.</span></span></span><br><span><span><span>As of March\, a
 ll BOTMDG Wednesday dances begin at <b>8 p.m. Eastern</b>.</span></span></s
 pan><br>&nbsp\;<br><span><span><span>If you haven’t been to one of our onli
 ne events\, you might be wondering what to expect! As our musicians play fo
 r us\, and the caller calls\, you are welcome to dance with us in your own 
 space\, play along with the musicians with your mic muted\, or just watch a
 nd listen. We also try to check in with everyone briefly each week. The mus
 ic lasts until about 8:45\, followed by the check-in.</span></span></span><
 br>&nbsp\;<br><span><span><span>Waltzes are easy to dance alone or with a p
 artner. Up-tempo tunes will sometimes have <span>contra</span>-like calling
 \, but for the times when there is no calling\, please feel free to dance a
 long at home with <span>contra</span> moves of your choice. Or just boogie 
 down to the amazing music!</span></span>&nbsp\; </span><br><br><span>------
 ----</span><span><br></span><br><span>We are grateful for all donations\, a
 nd happy to be able to keep paying our musicians and dance leaders during t
 hese unusual times. You can find our <a href="http://bloomingtoncontra.org/
 support-our-performers-during-the-covid-19-downtime/">PayPal donation butto
 n on our website</a>.&nbsp\;&nbsp\;&nbsp\; </span></span></span></span></sp
 an><br></span>
LAST-MODIFIED:20210328T145936Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Dancing through the Pundemic (Bob Green and Martha Edwards) (on Zoo
 m)
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
